7997 - Membership Sports and Recreation Clubs Summary > NORTH RYDE R S L COMMUNITY CLUB LTD is an Australian public company. Its operations cover membership sports and recreation clubs. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. NORTH RYDE R S L COMMUNITY CLUB LTD is headquartered in North Ryde, New South Wales. It is headed by general manager Richard Graham Reading. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $31.37 million. Its net profit totalled $2.58 million. NORTH RYDE R S L COMMUNITY CLUB LTD forms part of the services industry sector.
